---
source: crates/carta/tests/golden_e2e.rs
expression: output
---
A bullet list opens right after a paragraph line, with no blank between:

- apples
- pears

An ordered list interrupts the same way:

1.  second
2.  third

A parenthesized or roman marker has a list shape but no enabled style
here, so it breaks off as its own plain paragraph rather than folding
in:

(5) parenthesized

A decimal marker closed by a single paren stays prose and folds in, so
these two lines remain one paragraph: 1) not a list 2) still prose
